      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DASHING STARLET (3) made an impressive debut when well supported and ran up to expectations, showing a strong turn of foot to score a 2.5 lengths win at this track over 530m in 31.10. Looks promising and rates on top here on debut effort. NO EAR TRINDALL (1) is a progressive type who recorded his 5th career win last time out (31.13) at this track. Has never been out of the money in three starts this course. Won at his only start from this draw. In top form and looks a key chance again. LOVE SHINE (2) broke from this box and proved too strong to claim a Grade 6 win at this track in the fastest time of the card. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. MOLLEY MACALLAN (8) comes into calculations after placing most recently.",
